                            <br/>
                <h3 class="card-title">North Country National Scenic Trail</h3>
                <br/>
                <p>Come to the North Country. Trek the hills and valleys. Stand on the shores of lakes & streams from glaciers 10,000 years before. Clear-flowing water, red/gold of autumn, a fairyland of snow, open prairies, and distant horizons paint the land. Historic sites along the way tell how America settled and grew as a nation. From North Dakota to Vermont, adventure is never far away.</p>
                <div class="accordion" id="accordionExample">
