                            </button>
                        </h2>
                        <div id="collapseZero" class="accordion-collapse collapse" aria-labelledby="headingZero" data-bs-parent="#accordionExample">
                            <div class="accordion-body">
                                <p class="fst-italic">When complete, the North Country National Scenic Trail will be approximately 4,600 miles long. Currently, over 2,000 miles of trail are complete and waiting for you to use. Trail headquarters is based in Lowell, Michigan. Find North Country Trail Association's Maps and Trails Data to help you get there at https://northcountrytrail.org/trail/maps.</p>
